            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[费解]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_feijie-c1df37ef03.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%89%99%E7%BA%BF%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9%E7%89%99%E7%BC%9D%E5%8F%98%E5%AE%BD%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BB%8F%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E7%89%99%E7%BA%BF%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A9%E7%89%99%E7%BC%9D%E5%8F%98%E5%AE%BD%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#经常用牙线会让牙缝变宽吗#</span></a>】 卫，用牙线后，牙缝肉眼可见地变大咋办？emm……可能是你的牙缝原本就这么大。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>听卫说，如果不用牙线，牙缝中残留的食物残渣、软垢、牙菌斑没清理干净，可能会引发牙周炎、牙龈萎缩等疾病，反而让牙缝越来越大！赶紧戳图了解牙线👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2sk310j20p01egtfl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2sgq6vj20p00kztbd.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2shpx3j20p00oo77b.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2shxp1j20p00sjtc2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2sjew9j20p00p0acb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2sj4jaj20p01fxgrg.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2slh7wj20p02bw47k.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2sj72uj20j60le76n.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hisb2sie1oj20j60ki0ul.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
